criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Patients seeking treatment at the Obesity Unit of the Hospital Medica Sur, Mexico
             City, Mexico

          2. a Body Mass Index higher than 40;

          3. written and informed consent to participate.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. other concurrent severe psychiatric disturbances (psychosis, depression with suicidal
             risk, alcohol or drug abuse);

          2. concurrent medical condition not related to the disorder;

          3. one or more failures in following an obesity treatment.
